'''龐雪麗'''<ref name="星島201123"/><ref name="明報201124"/> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|MLA}} （{{lang|en|Shirley Bond}}，1956/1957年－<ref>P.G. Mount Robson's Liberal candidates: Party members choose their candidate Friday and Saturday: [Final Edition]
Hoekstra, Gordon. Prince George Citizen [Prince George, B.C] 27 Sep 2000: 5.</ref>），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，2020年起出任[[卑詩省|卑詩省]]官方反對黨主席，2020年-22年間任職[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]]臨時黨魁。她從2001年起以卑詩自由黨黨員身份先後擔任[[卑詩省議會|卑詩省議會]]喬治王子城－洛遜山選區和喬治王子城－維爾芒特選區議員，並曾在前[[卑詩省省長|省長]][[戈登·坎贝尔|金寶爾]]和[[簡蕙芝|簡蕙芝]]的內閣中出任數項廳長職務，當中包括於2004年-09年間任職[[卑詩省副省長|卑詩省副省長]]。

==生平==
龐雪麗於[[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[喬治王子城|喬治王子城]]出生<ref name="PGFP081007"/>，曾三度當選喬治王子城學校局學務委員，並於最後一屆學委任期出任該局主席<ref name="BCLeg41">{{cite web |url=https://www.leg.bc.ca/learn-about-us/members/41st-Parliament/Bond-Shirley |title=41st Parliament Members at dissolution on September 21, 2020: Hon. Shirley Bond |publisher=[[卑詩省議會|卑詩省議會]] |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427220005/https://www.leg.bc.ca/learn-about-us/members/41st-Parliament/Bond-Shirley |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="about">{{cite web |url=https://bcliberalcaucus.bc.ca/mla/shirley-bond/ |title=About Shirley |publisher=[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]] |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202065841/https://bcliberalcaucus.bc.ca/mla/shirley-bond/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她於2001年省選代表[[卑詩自由黨|卑詩自由黨]]競逐喬治王子城－洛遜山選區（{{lang|en|Prince George-Mount Robson}}）議席並告當選，首度晉身[[卑詩省議會|省議會]]，並獲省長[[戈登·坎贝尔|金寶爾]]任命為專上教育廳長<ref name="BCLeg41"/><ref name="about"/>。她於2004年12月改任卑詩省副省長，接替請辭的[[簡蕙芝|簡蕙芝]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.pgfreepress.com/bond-appointed-new-deputy-premier/ |title=Bond appointed new deputy premier |publisher=''Prince George Free Press'' |date=2004-09-23 |accessdate=2020-12-11 }}</ref>，並兼任衛生服務廳長<ref name="PGM201123">{{cite news |url=https://www.princegeorgematters.com/local-news/prince-george-valemount-mla-shirley-bond-elected-interim-leader-of-bc-liberals-2903486 |title=Prince George-Valemount MLA Shirley Bond elected interim leader of BC Liberals |publisher=Prince George Matters |first=Kyle |last=Balzer |date=2020-11-23 |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123211410/https://www.princegeorgematters.com/local-news/prince-george-valemount-mla-shirley-bond-elected-interim-leader-of-bc-liberals-2903486 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她於2005年省選連任喬治王子城－洛遜山選區省議員，在金寶爾內閣留任副省長，並兼任教育廳長<ref name="PGM201123"/>。喬治王子城－洛遜山選區於2009年省選改組成喬治王子城－維爾芒特選區（{{lang|en|Prince George-Valemount}}），龐雪麗在該選區連任省議員，在金寶爾內閣中改任運輸及基建廳長<ref name="PGM201123"/>。簡蕙芝於2011年取代金寶爾出任省長後，龐雪麗調任公共安全廳長和檢察總長<ref name="PGM201123"/>。隨著律政廳長彭百里（{{lang|en|Barry Penner}}）於2011年8月請辭<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/barry-penner-steps-down-as-b-c-s-attorney-general-1.980883 |title=Barry Penner steps down as B.C.'s attorney general |date=2011-08-18 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2020-12-12 }}</ref>，簡蕙芝委派龐雪麗出任該職，成為卑詩省首位女性律政廳長<ref name="星島201123">{{cite news |url=https://www.singtao.ca/4624079/2020-11-23/news-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E7%9C%81%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%BE%90%E9%9B%AA%E9%BA%97%E7%8D%B2%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B8%E7%82%BA%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98/?variant=zh-hk |title=資深省議員龐雪麗獲推選為卑詩自由黨臨時黨領 |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2020-11-23 |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124054909/https://www.singtao.ca/4624079/2020-11-23/news-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E7%9C%81%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%BE%90%E9%9B%AA%E9%BA%97%E7%8D%B2%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B8%E7%82%BA%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/shirley-bond-bc-liberals-interim-leader-1.5813030 |title=Veteran MLA Shirley Bond chosen interim leader of the B.C. Liberal Party |date=2020-11-23 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2021-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929175127/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/shirley-bond-bc-liberals-interim-leader-1.5813030 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她於2013年省選連任省議員後，在簡蕙芝內閣中改任就業、旅遊及技能培訓廳長<ref name="PGM201123"/>。

龐雪麗於2017年5月9日舉行的省選中連任省議員，然而自由黨只贏取省議會87個議席中的43席，無法繼續以多數政府姿態執政。在此[[懸峙國會|懸峙議會]]局面下，簡蕙芝於同年6月組閣，龐雪麗留任原本廳長職務<ref name="Sun170612">{{cite news |url=http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/christy-clark-will-be-sworn-in-as-b-c-premier-today |title=B.C. Premier Christy Clark introduces new cabinet |publisher=《溫哥華太陽報》 |date=2017-06-12 |accessdate=2018-02-05 |first=Scott |last=Brown |archive-date=2017-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119145257/http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/christy-clark-will-be-sworn-in-as-b-c-premier-today |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="星島170613">{{cite news|title=簡蕙芝組短命內閣華裔僅屈潔冰留任|accessdate=2018-02-08|newspaper=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版|date=2017-06-13|url=http://www.singtao.ca/vancouver/1197911/2017-06-13/post-%E7%B0%A1%E8%95%99%E8%8A%9D%E7%B5%84%E7%9F%AD%E5%91%BD%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E5%83%85%E5%B1%88%E6%BD%94%E5%86%B0%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB/?variant=zh-hk}}</ref>。持有41席的新民主黨與持有3席的綠黨達成合作協議，並於同年6月29日在省議會向自由黨政府提出[[不信任動議|不信任動議]]。動議以44-42票通過，自由黨遂失去執政權<ref name="CBC170629a">{{cite news|title=B.C. Liberal government loses confidence vote 44-42, sparking either NDP government or election|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-liberals-fall-non-confidence-1.4185005|accessdate=2017-06-30|publisher=CBC News|date=2017-06-29|first=Justin|last=McElroy|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104160802/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-liberals-fall-non-confidence-1.4185005|dead-url=no}}</ref>，龐雪麗的廳長任期亦隨著新民主黨少數政府於同年7月就任而終結。此後她出任官方反對黨財政共同評議員，以及省議會公共帳目常務委員會主席<ref name="BCLeg41"/><ref name="about"/>。

2020年10月24日省選，龐雪麗再度連任省議員，但自由黨只贏取28席，較選前減少13席。[[韋勤信|韋勤信]]於選後兩日宣布辭任黨魁<ref name="星島201026">{{cite news |url=https://www.singtao.ca/4569738/2020-10-26/news-%E9%9F%8B%E5%8B%A4%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%AD%E5%8E%BB%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E4%B8%80%E8%81%B7/?variant=zh-hk |title=韋勤信宣布辭去自由黨黨領一職 |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2020-10-26 |accessdate=2020-12-10 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027100651/https://www.singtao.ca/4569738/2020-10-26/news-%e9%9f%8b%e5%8b%a4%e4%bf%a1%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e8%be%ad%e5%8e%bb%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e9%bb%a8%e9%bb%a8%e9%a0%98%e4%b8%80%e8%81%b7/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref>，自由黨黨團則於同年11月23日選出龐雪麗為臨時黨魁<ref name="星島201123"/><ref name="明報201124">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20201124/vad4_r.htm |title=龐雪麗當選卑詩自由黨臨時黨領 |publisher=《明報》加西網 |date=2020-11-24 |accessdate=2020-12-12 }}</ref>。她於同月30日公布官方反對黨影子內閣名單，她本人兼任長者服務和長期護理事務評議員<ref name="about"/><ref name="PGM201201">{{cite news |url=https://www.princegeorgematters.com/local-news/bc-liberals-interim-leader-and-prince-george-valemount-mla-shirley-bond-announces-shadow-cabinet-3143582 |title=BC Liberals' Interim Leader and Prince George-Valemount MLA Shirley Bond announces shadow cabinet |publisher=Prince George Matters |first=Jess |last=Fedigan |date=2020-12-01 |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205121949/https://www.princegeorgematters.com/local-news/bc-liberals-interim-leader-and-prince-george-valemount-mla-shirley-bond-announces-shadow-cabinet-3143582 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨著[[馮宜幹|馮宜幹]]於2022年2月5日當選自由黨黨魁<ref>{{cite news|title=馮宜幹成功當選卑詩自由黨黨領 |url=https://www.singtao.ca/5549850/2022-02-05/news-%E9%A6%AE%E5%AE%9C%E5%B9%B9%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%91%E8%A9%A9%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98/ |publisher=《星島日報》加西版|author=王弘樹|access-date=2022-02-07|date=2022-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Former cabinet minister Kevin Falcon wins B.C. Liberal leadership race on 5th ballot|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/former-cabinet-minister-kevin-falcon-wins-b-c-liberal-leadership-race-on-5th-ballot-1.6341317|publisher=The Canadian Press, via CBC News|access-date=2022-02-07|date=2022-02-05|first1=Dirk|last1=Meissner|first2=Brieanna|last2=Charlebois|archive-date=2022-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220207133620/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/former-cabinet-minister-kevin-falcon-wins-b-c-liberal-leadership-race-on-5th-ballot-1.6341317|dead-url=no}}</ref>，龐雪麗亦卸任臨時黨魁。

龐雪麗從喬治王子城的{{le|新喀里多尼亞學院|College of New Caledonia}}畢業，並曾於[[北英屬哥倫比亞大學|北英屬哥倫比亞大學]]修讀政治學，但當選省議員後退學<ref>{{cite web |url=https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/archive/2001-2005/2004otp0095-001079-attachment1.htm |title=BIOGRAPHIES |publisher=卑詩省政府 |accessdate=2020-12-14 |date=2004-12-14 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153411/https://archive.news.gov.bc.ca/releases/archive/2001-2005/2004otp0095-001079-attachment1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她丈夫比爾於2020年中風後去世，兩人育有兩名子女<ref name="PGC200609"/>。

